<br>
I (and my guild, House Arcane) invite anyone who is available to come out and help this coming Sunday.  However, if possible, I ask that you be at least 55+ and non-kos to Coldain (I do NOT like excluding people, but if we have TOO many under 55, it will only create added lag/ld issues.  Also, there will be a kos to Coldain camp, so if you want to help and you are kos, we will make sure you are put with them.  Again, tho, prefer non-kos, but not a big deal, <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )<br>
<br>
We have established looting rules for the items awarded for each Coldain Hero that is kept alive.  They are as follows:<br>
<br>
1.) The quester shall select 1 item to do with as he/she sees fit (ie. he/she may keep it for him/herself or award to someone else)<br>
2.) Guilds with 6 or more lvl 55+ representatives shall receive 1 random per item until/unless it wins something, after which it shall abstain from further randoming.<br>
3.) All lvl 55+ present who are NOT in a guild with at least 6 lvl 55+ representatives, shall be combined to form 1 randoming block.  Again, if/when this block wins a random, it shall abstain from further randoming. <br>
The guilds/block that win an item, can decide for themselves how to sub-random it, <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I look forward to seeing many of you this Sunday!<br>
<br>
